nodes.text: Docking Bay 63 was a privately owned docking bay located on Ord Mynock in the Ord Mynock Freeport. It was able to accommodate starships up the size of a medium freighter. It was also the docking bay located closest to the center of Ord Mynock Freeport. The docking bay had the standard assortment of equipment to refuel a ship, repair damage, and clean and refresh life support systems.
